
# Ignore everything by default
/*


# Allowlist core dotfiles
!system/
!.gitignore
!README.md
!install.sh
!autostart/
!hypr/
!waybar/
!waypaper/
!kitty/
!rofi/
!mako/
!qt6ct/
!gtk-3.0/
!gtk-4.0/
!flameshot/
!networkmanager-dmenu/
!snmenu/
!xsettingsd/
!mimeapps.list
!user-dirs.dirs
!user-dirs.locale
!accsiart.txt

# Optional allowlist (enable if you decide to track these)
#!zsh/
#!nvim/
#!alacritty/
#!tmux/
#!git/

# Keep Kvantum empty (do not track themes)
!Kvantum/
Kvantum/*
!Kvantum/.gitkeep

# Always ignore app data roots
BraveSoftware/
Code/
Code - OSS/
mozilla/
spotify/
dconf/
pulse/
session/
go/telemetry/
yay/
wireshark/
QtProject.conf

# Common junk and generated files
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*.bak
**/*.lock
**/*~
**/*.sqlite
**/*.db
**/*.ldb
**/*.journal

# Browser/Chromium-style data
**/Cache/**
**/cache/**
**/Code Cache/**
**/GPUCache/**
**/Crashpad/**
**/Service Worker/**
**/Session Storage/**
**/Local Storage/**
**/IndexedDB/**
**/Cookies*
**/Network Persistent State
**/Local State
**/Preferences
**/History

# Secrets and credentials
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.pem
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx
**/*.kdbx
**/*.key
**/id_rsa
**/id_rsa.pub
**/id_ed25519
**/id_ed25519.pub
**/known_hosts
**/authorized_keys
**/.gnupg/**
**/credentials
**/secrets.yml
**/secrets.yaml

